text:
You made it on time,
It's good to see your face before the recording.

Sorry for keeping you waiting...!
But it's good to see both of you looking relaxed.

Do you think so?
But both Haruki-chan and I were shaking until just now.

We tried lots of ways
to relax and loosen up...

Ah, Hana-chan,
Luca-chan, they went ahead of us~...!
